Package: EBSmoothr
Type: Package
Title: Empirical Bayes Smoothing with L-GP and Matern Priors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "EBSmoothr", "Developers",
      email = "devnull@example.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Author: EBSmoothr Developers [aut, cre]
Maintainer: EBSmoothr Developers <devnull@example.com>
Description: Provides empirical Bayes smoothers for Gaussian means using
    local Gaussian-process (L-GP) and Matern spatial priors. Supports
    known-noise `ebnm` workflows through `ebnm_LGP_generator()` and
    `ebnm_Matern_generator()`, and a higher-level `eb_smoother()`
    interface that can also learn one common observation noise SD when
    standard errors are unknown. Includes a constant Gaussian baseline,
    point-mass reference families, spatial scoring wrappers, TMB backends
    for L-GP and Matern Laplace models, and exact Gaussian / INLA-SPDE
    backends for Matern models.
